{"word":"H2560 - חָמַר - châmar - khaw-mar' - Daub - பூசு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>חָמַר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châmar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-mar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Daub / பூசு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பூசு, சிவந்திரு, பொங்கு, அழுக்கடை, கொதித்திரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to boil, to foam, to foam up, to ferment"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to boil, to foam up"},{"paragraph":"b) (Poalal) to be troubled, to be in turmoil"},{"paragraph":"2) (Poalal) to be reddened"},{"paragraph":"3) (Qal) to danb, seal up, to cover or smear with asphalt"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>boil</i> up; hence to <i>ferment</i> (with scum); to <i>glow</i> (with redness); as denominative (from <a href=\"#/H2564 - חֵמָר - chêmâr - khay-mawr'/2564\">H2564</a>) to <i>smear</i> with pitch: - daub, foul, be red, trouble."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2543 - חֲמֹור - chămôwr - kham-ore'/2543\">H2543</a>, <a href=\"#/H2544 - חֲמֹור - Chămôwr - kham-ore'/2544\">H2544</a>, <a href=\"#/H2560 - חָמַר - châmar - khaw-mar'/2560\">H2560</a>, <a href=\"#/H2561 - חֶמֶר - chemer - kheh'-mer/2561\">H2561</a>, <a href=\"#/H2563 - חֹמֶר - chômer - kho'mer/2563\">H2563</a>, <a href=\"#/H2564 - חֵמָר - chêmâr - khay-mawr'/2564\">H2564</a>, <a href=\"#/H2566 - חַמְרָן - Chamrân - kham-rawn'/2566\">H2566</a>, <a href=\"#/H3180 - יַחְמוּר - yachmûwr - yakh-moor'/3180\">H3180</a>"}]}